{
  "stem": "942.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Nazis started this brainwashing, because, almost instantly, and perhaps a few days after we arrived there, this SS officer came into the brickyard, and he made a speech.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was telling us in Hungarian and German that we're going to be resettled in the east.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, he said this every day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said that families will be together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you can take everything you have with you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, we didn't have much, but you know, when you have that little, you know, it becomes all of a sudden a big possession, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I realize that now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you're sort of holding onto something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It-- it-- it ties you to your home, and it gives you some security.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So but when they said, your families will be together, and your work-- you'll be working together, that really sounded good, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we sort of couldn't wait to come to this promised land, you know, wherever that was, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We thought it was Eastern Hungary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We never thought it was going to be in Poland, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So this went on for about a good 2 weeks, this brainwashing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And eventually, finally, the transports started to leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I think there were three transports that left from this brickyard in Kassa.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when the transports were leaving, they were asking for-- for kids to come and clean up the mess, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "People leave a lot of trash and stuff behind, and we had to clean up everything to, sort of like, to wipe out all the evidence, you know, that was left behind, you know?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you know, we found some coins and things that people dropped from their pockets, and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
